{"tid":2243850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［呃哂］消委會：有「001」安全套實際係0.054  廠商：0.01只是型號名稱 與厚度無關","createTime":"2020-10-15T05:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T15:04:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8dcd73f3540dc44d2d9d7768516b98513ac90913","tid":2243850,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:06:30.000Z","msg":"近年不少安全套都以「薄」為宣傳重點，消費者委員會最新測試9個牌子共30款安全套，物理性能整體表現滿意，但樣本間的厚薄度可相差逾4倍，即使同樣聲稱「超薄」的樣本，其厚度亦相差逾倍。消委會亦檢視各樣本的包裝和標示，約三分之一的樣本均以例如「0.01」、「0.02」、「0.03」等數字作招徠，但部份沒有標明單位，也沒有註明數字代表產品厚度，有可能令消費者聯想與產品厚度相關⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n例如8款（27%）型號在包裝上標示了「0.01」、「001」、「0.02」等數字，但不是每款都有列出量度單位，亦不是每款都有說明是代表厚度。例如「Aoni」2款樣本在包裝上列出「001」這組數字，沒有單位或小數點，量得的厚度分別為0.054及0.055毫米，而代理商回覆時表示，從來未聲稱過「001」與產品厚度有任何關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201015/ZTGFZKLPDNFBHN7MCGB5QTZHSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201015%2FZTGFZKLPDNFBHN7MCGB5QTZHSE%2F&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=f67f7fcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201015%2FZTGFZKLPDNFBHN7MCGB5QTZHSE%2F&h=7568b099\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201015/ZTGFZKLPDNFBHN7MCGB5QTZHSE/</a>"},{"pid":"002ba598918035195a8f1050b9737f9c1f9df0f3","tid":2243850,"uid":353330,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"菠蘿包冇菠蘿"},{"pid":"d3dcfcd44ed9ec70d0c66cd4a01a440c826062ac","tid":2243850,"uid":109923,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"我個龜頭已經磨到戴套冇feel射唔出，一定要無套先爽"},{"pid":"78856811835a02a7dd0618db215a35c92905cb2b","tid":2243850,"uid":41204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:10:21.000Z","msg":"好認真咁去度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ec90111e27209e9b61b517c7f1e6c5ddb0045d","tid":2243850,"uid":345221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quo